ung gesellschaftlicher Machtfragen sichtbar.  aThe daily work of hygienic cleanliness - an ethnography of the negotiation of social order in the hospital.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aAffekttheorie. 4aArbeit. 4aArbeits- und Industriesoziologie. 4aEthnografie. 4aGender. 4aHygiene. 4aKrankenhaus. 4aMedizin. 4aRaumtheorie. 4aReinigung. 4aSauberkeit. 4aSoziale Ungleichheit. 4aSoziologie. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aCleaning.  aEthnography.  aGender.  aHospital.  aHygiene.  aMedicine.  aSocial Inequality.  aSociology of Work and Industry.  aSociology.  aSpatial Theory.  aWork.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2017z9783110548242oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839438114zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839438114423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839438114/original  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DSWb2017